reviews.text:
Really great recipe man, me and a friend of mine who I mix for, always have a 100ml bottle of this brewing up.&#xD;
I also like to sub the maple with tfa 2.5% or a combo of both. Really only played with them cause I keep running out.&#xD;
Great stuff

Hey SlashaLo! I wanted to let you know, I watched the maple notes video and they talked about your maple vanilla long john you mixed for the mixathon that you did for someone who wanted a very maple recipe.&#xD;
&#xD;
Guess what! It was me who asked! You mixed it for me! So I wanted to say I use it a lot and it’s nice. I think when I know how to mix better I might tweak it a bit so the maple is a little less dry and the vanilla doesn’t come through as much but I still totally love it. It ages really well and I always have a 60ml of it aging somewhere.
